T :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br><br><br>Emeric<br>Prexus <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/usehnsuch.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sehnsuch</A> at: 9/17/02 5:17:23 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#cccccc><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/udreamswalker.showPublicProfile?language=EN>DreamsWalker</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Young Grasshoppah</span><br>  Posts: 20<br> <font color=#8b1a1a>(9/17/02 8:25:30 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=11464.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Sarnak Warhammer - What the...</span><hr size=1> bump, I would like to know also be considering buying one also, they go for around 6k on karana. <p>Yizelar Kontrol<br>Level 59 Enchanter<br>Baron Boundry Wardenn<br>Level 51 Monk<br>Jagjang Highlander<br>Level 50 Shaman<br>Overlords of Darkness<br></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#778899><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/bmonklybusiness43508.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=kensha>kensha</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Young Grasshoppah</span><br>  Posts: 1<br> <font color=#8b1a1a>(9/17/02 8:55:58 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=11464.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> sarnak warhammer</span><hr size=1> Good proc, no DD , just stun. Its good for the poorer monks like me for solo work. Stun proc = dmg avoidance. Stuns for 3-4 seconds <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#cccccc><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/usavagermonk.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Savager Monk</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Monk</span><br>  Posts: 189<br> <font color=#8b1a1a>(9/17/02 9:32:20 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=11464.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://pic1.picturetrail.com/VOL124/526649/1034240/12713891.ptp WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Sarnak Warhammer - What the...</span><hr size=1> I used that have that weapon, I loved it until I got my Tranquil Staff.  I think it's definately better than JM and it's really cool looking weapon.<br><br>Savager<br>LVL58 Povar <p><center><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=250625><img src=http://pic1.picturetrail.com/VOL124/526649/1034240/12731490.ptp></center></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#778899><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/udelnathapowa.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Delnatha Powa</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Monk</span><br>  Posts: 125<br> <font color=#8b1a1a>(9/18/02 8:02:19 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=11464.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> well...</span><hr size=1> I have one now but I eventually moved it to my warrior twink.  I looked for one forever and would auction for it and people always would try to sell me a sarnak battlehammer instead.  The reason you don't hear much about it is because it drops in disco area in seblis but it is a very rare drop. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#cccccc><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/udalarianwashere.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Dalarian was here</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Monk-in-Training</span><br>  Posts: 75<br> <font color=#8b1a1a>(9/18/02 9:31:07 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=11464.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: well...</span><hr size=1> Paid 1500 for mine, I like it and its probably worth a little more than 1500 (on RN the Jade Mace seems to run around 2500 to 3k). Been trying to scrape up enough for a BoRS (I like stun stuff) but I hardly ever see them for sale. Of course, I think the warhammer I have is one of two I've seen for sale in the bazaar, so in that light the BoRS (I think I've seen 3 or 4) isn't quite as rare.<br><br>Downsides: <br>Dual wielding kinda sucks for soloing unless you're farming greenies.<br><br>Most of the time in a group/raid a JM would be a better weapon, unless you're the tank.<br><br>JM is alot easier to find.<br><br>It only has an 'average' proc rate. No tash stick level procc'ing.<br><br>Positives:<br>The stun is nice farming greenies/casters.<br><br>The damage avoided during stun helps even out the extra ripostes you take from dual wielding.<br><br>It looks cool. =p<br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#778899><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uddubois.showPublicProfile?language=EN>ddubois</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Disciple</span><br>  Posts: 276<br> <font color=#8b1a1a>(9/18/02 9:57:14 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=11464.topic&index=6>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Modals</span><hr size=1> SWh: (9+9+11)/20 = 1.45<br>BoRS: (11+11+11)/22 = 1.5<br><br>So if you 1h damage bonus is 11, it was a worse modal than BoRS.  If you're damage bonus is smaller, the weapon becomes even worse, relatively speaking.<br><br>AC: (15+15+11)/25 = 1.64<br><br>Adamanite Club beats them both, and the proc is 6 second fixed duration stun with 60dd.<br> <p><B>Daniel DuBois</B><br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=47010">Munnk Twinnk</a> <i>- Level 60 Grandmaster of Tholuxe Paells</i><br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=3641">Master Mezitt</a> <i>- Level 60 Phantasmist of Tholuxe Paells</i><br></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#cccccc><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/udalarianwashere.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Dalarian was here</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Monk-in-Training</span><br>  Posts: 76<br> <font color=#8b1a1a>(9/18/02 11:01:31 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=11464.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Modals</span><hr size=1> Adamanite Club and BoRS have the same proc though, so add the DD on the stun component + the 2 second longer stun and the BoRS blows the Warhammer out of the water. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm3.showPrevMessage?topicID=11464.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm3.showNextMessage?topicID=11464.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=11464.topic&index=7><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm3.emailToFriend